      <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="DSC_0150.JPG"/>Hrn <hi rend="latintype">Doctor
                  Richard</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb338" type="place">I Wollzeile 15</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="DSC_0151.JPG"/>Lieber Richard!</salute></opener><p><rs ref="#pmb18523" type="person">Paul Horn</rs> hat abgeſchrieben, ich theils bei <hi rend="latintype">Frau <rs ref="#pmb16312" type="person">Fl.</rs></hi> mit.</p><p>Alſo morgen iſt nichts.&#160;–</p><p>Wann ſehn wir uns wieder? Ich kann in der <date>Sylveſternacht</date> ſehr ſpät ins
                  <rs ref="#pmb49" type="place">Pfob</rs>, ſo um <time>2</time>. Herzlichst</p><closer>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body>
